17
00:00:50,650 --> 00:00:51,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana perasaanku?</font>

18
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:55,900
<font color=#FFFF00>"Aku gagal dalam hidup ini."</font>

19
00:00:56,550 --> 00:00:59,440
<font color=#FFFF00>"Aku lebih suka mengakhiri hidupku..."</font>

20
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:01,010
