83
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Asisten?</font>

84
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:28,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Asisten Lee Ru Ri!</font>

85
00:04:28,150 --> 00:04:30,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan melakukan
apapun yang kau suruh.</font>

86
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Hormat!</font>

87
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:36,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa tamu istimewa itu?</font>

88
