<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

103
00:05:23,150 --> 00:05:24,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan, "Cookie".</font>

104
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:30,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Cookie.</font>

105
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu. Tunggu aku.</font>

106
00:05:37,530 --> 00:05:38,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi.</font>

107
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:40,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

108
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:41,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo.</font>

109
00:05:43,910 --> 00:05:45,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa, sayang? Apa?</font>

