113
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,300
<font color=#FFFF00>...mempersiapkan acara lamaran yang bagus.</font>

114
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:55,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

115
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:57,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih atas bantuanmu.</font>

116
