117
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:02,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo.</font>

118
00:06:07,530 --> 00:06:08,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Daebak!</font>

119
00:06:12,900 --> 00:06:16,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia gadis itu, 'kan? Orang yang
