<font color=#FFFF00>Apa...</font>

121
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:25,960
<font color=#FFFF00>"Klub Pasangan, Lee Ru Ri"?</font>

122
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:30,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Mohon tunggu sebentar.</font>

123
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Daebak.</font>

124
00:06:32,650 --> 00:06:36,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kupikir kita harus meminta orang lain
untuk membantu acara lamaran kita.</font>

125
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Rasanya aneh mantan pacarku
