126
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:41,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar, 'kan?</font>

127
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, tidak sama sekali.</font>

128
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:45,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa Oppa tidak nyaman dengan itu?</font>

129
00:06:45,700 --> 00:06:49,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, berarti kau
